      "grammarNote": "Adverb form: felizmente (happily). Spanish adverbs are made by adding -mente to the feminine adjective. Feliz has no gender change: feliz + mente → felizmente. E.g., 'Ella sonrió felizmente.' (She smiled happily.)",
